6
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:05,160
Esperad a ver

7
00:00:05,160 --> 00:00:05,480
lo que me he

8
00:00:05,480 --> 00:00:06,240
encontrado hoy

9
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:07,200
en Benimaclet.

10
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:08,440
Salgo con la bici...

11
00:00:08,440 --> 00:00:08,880
y lo veo

12
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:09,680
a menudo.

13
00:00:09,680 --> 00:00:10,240
Aparatos que

14
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,520
