33
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:26,280
Os enseño.

34
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,560
Hoy me encontré dos.

35
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:28,120
Uno ya había

36
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:28,960
