49
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:40,200
Funcionando.

50
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:41,600
Esa es la diferencia.

51
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:42,280
Lo que se comparte

52
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,160
